name: AUDIENCE

description: Stores detailed content for a brief, linked exclusively to an intervention.

schema.description: Links to the associated intervention.

schema.description: The client or funding organization for the brief.

schema.description: The primary challenge addressed by the brief.

schema.description: The initial objective for the brief.

schema.description: A list of 'don't' guidelines for the brief.

schema.description: The currency of the allocated budget (e.g., 'USD').

schema.description: The target completion date for the brief.

schema.description: The suggested type of intervention for the brief.

schema.name: donts
schema.description: This column will store a list of texts for don'ts.
